        "subject": "LU-5448 cfs: Fix compilation without libreadline",
        "message": "LU-5448 cfs: Fix compilation without libreadline\n\nThe two void declarations added by LU-5418\n(http://review.whamcloud.com/11231):\nstatic void noop_int_fn(int unused) { }\nstatic void noop_void_fn(void) { }\n\nAre not used if HAVE_LIBREADLINE is not defined, which\nresults in a compilation error.\n\nFix is easy, just wrap those declarations in\nifdef HAVE_LIBREADLINE.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: Ia250a97303ed12f84d88cd48ec3794caae17d222\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
